

At the top of the file you can tweak constants:

SMOOTHING — 0..1 smoothing factor (lower = smoother)

MOVE_GAIN_X, MOVE_GAIN_Y — horizontal and vertical sensitivity multipliers

LEFT_CLICK_COOLDOWN, RIGHT_CLICK_COOLDOWN — minimum seconds between click events

EAR_BLINK_THR, EAR_OPEN_THR — eye aspect ratio thresholds for blink/wink detection

SHOW_OVERLAY — show debug overlay (set to False for production)

USE_LEFT_EYE_FOR_CURSOR — choose left eye only or average of both eyes for cursor position
